column1: Predation (Mpred), Starvation (Mstarv), Other Natural mortality (Mnat), Fishing (F) & Out-of-domain (Zout) mortality rates per time step of saving, except for Mnat Eggs that is expressed in osmose time step. Z is the total mortality for migratory fish outside the simulation grid. To get annual mortality rates, sum the mortality rates within one year.
